	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />UNROM is CHR RAM, so there is no CHR file to combine.  
<br />
<br />The other way is to start with a .nes file, and only keep the first 16 bytes.  Then paste in your PRG followed by your CHR.  Use an app like Nintendulator which has a iNES header editor.  There you can enter in the correct values for mapper and prg/chr sizes.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


