	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Bumping this up because I figured out what I was doing wrong and it may help others avoid the same mistake.
<br />
<br />I was putting my .prg files and .chr files in their corresponding folders in the CopyNES directory.  In order to combine a .chr with a .prg file, they need to not only be named the same thing, but also located in the same folder.  If not, you end up getting a shit .nes file.
<br />
<br />Thanks for the help guys, I really appreciate it!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
